criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  It meets the 2019 ACR/EULAR classification diagnostic criteria for IgG4 related
             diseases, and is an active IgG4-RD, defined as an IgG4-RD RI score ≥ 3 points when
             screening

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  1. IgG4 related diseases endangering organ function or life;

             2. Only Mikulicz disease, no other internal organs involved;

             3. People with history of thrombotic disease or high risk of thrombosis;

             4. Have a history of malignant tumor;

             5. Active infection;

             6. Pregnant or lactating women;
